Welcome to my automatic farming bot for Clash of Clans.

Screenshot on the wiki: https://github.com/CodeSlinger69/ClAsHbOt/wiki

Key features:
- Anti-detection
- Auto raid, including troop queuing
- Auto Dark Elixir zapping
- Maintain trophy range
- Snipable town hall search (for pushing)

Why I wrote this bot: https://github.com/CodeSlinger69/ClAsHbOt/wiki/History

Walkthrough of the bot and its interface: https://github.com/CodeSlinger69/ClAsHbOt/wiki/Walkthrough

Anti-ban: https://github.com/CodeSlinger69/ClAsHbOt/wiki/Anti-detection-and-anti-ban

Botting caution: https://github.com/CodeSlinger69/ClAsHbOt/wiki/Botting-and-open-source




